        {
            "title": "財經｜政府暫停籃球博彩  李家超：預測市場超出預期急速發展",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜政府暫停籃球博彩 李家超：預測市場超出預期急速發展\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜政府暫停籃球博彩 李家超：預測市場超出預期急速發展</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">行政長官李家超今早出席行會前重申，預測市場（Prediction Market）「超出預期急速發展」，政府不應忽視風險而盲目推進籃球博彩等新項目，強調這類非法賭博平台過去兩年增速驚人，當中高達40%交易涉及體育賽事，每月交易量由2024年初少於1億美元，至2025年底暴增至130億美元，全年總額達640億美元（約5000億港元），分析預計2030年再增5倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">民政及青年事務局早前宣布煞停原定9月由香港賽馬會推出的籃球博彩試行計劃，擔心會間接助長預測市場非法活動。證監會投委會亦於4月17日首次明確指，香港參與預測市場交易「可能構成非法賭博」，無任何監管保障。李家超重申政府一貫不鼓勵賭博立場，須全面審視風險效益後先考慮新博彩項目，馬會已表示尊重決定並靜候進一步指示。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-569678d6-0760-3c2b-bb7a-39d03c2641a6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%83%E7%90%83%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E8%B6%85%E5%87%BA%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E6%80%A5%E9%80%9F%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95-083017695.html",
