            "title": "首岸第1期原價加推120伙｜折實均呎19,940元｜同柱單位加幅約1.28%至3.79%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒地牽頭發展的紅磡庇利街大型重建項目首岸第1期，繼上周二（14日）公布首張價單、涉及110伙後，發展商昨天（20日）再公布第2號價單，加推120伙。新一批單位折實均呎19,940元，較首張價單的18,666元高約6.83%；若按同座同柱單位比較，實際加幅僅介乎1.28%至3.79%，屬原價加推。發展商預告短期內將公布銷售安排。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"首岸第1期價單\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:首岸第1期價單;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4swq7yQ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">首岸第1期價單</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【新盤消息】首岸第1期首批均呎18,666元 貼近同區新盤定價｜兩房入場呎價高啟岸逾4%\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【新盤消息】首岸第1期首批均呎18,666元 貼近同區新盤定價｜兩房入場呎價高啟岸逾4%;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4tWfy9z\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【新盤消息】首岸第1期首批均呎18,666元 貼近同區新盤定價｜兩房入場呎價高啟岸逾4%</a></p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-940ff66c-73cf-3e59-af71-2a715d9fe079-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"首匯首輪成功沽出96%｜DEEP WATER SOUTH次輪僅售22%｜太古城三房戶持貨42年轉售 升值逾22倍\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:首匯首輪成功沽出96%｜DEEP WATER SOUTH次輪僅售22%｜太古城三房戶持貨42年轉售 升值逾22倍;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4soXWBQ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">首匯首輪成功沽出96%｜DEEP WATER SOUTH次輪僅售22%｜太古城三房戶持貨42年轉售 升值逾22倍</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>主打兩房  折實均呎19,940元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第2號價單涉及120伙，全數位於第2座，涵蓋115伙兩房戶及5伙三房戶，以兩房為主打，實用面積介乎339至642平方呎。按定價計算，整批單位市值約9.98億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">扣除最高9%折扣優惠後，折實售價約648.01萬至1,315.76萬元，折實呎價約18,360至21,158元，折實均呎為19,940元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>兩房折實入場費648萬元起</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩房入場單位為第2座5樓M室，實用面積339平方呎，折實售價約648.01萬元，折實呎價約19,115元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cFs3a70f2Si9pnDM3qSPlQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/2d8127d43977631c72d130db4dd454ca\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>兩房入場單位：第2座5樓M室平面圖</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>三房折實入場費1,231萬元起</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三房入場單位為第2座17樓A室，實用面積642平方呎，折實售價約1,231.23萬元，折實呎價約19,178元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1rxt2OIXachfFKo7.Hp1ww--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/b8dcb1edae33197ba83c0f36ad5157e3\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>三房入場單位：第2座17樓A室平面圖</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>折實呎價介乎1.84萬至2.12萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">整批單位當中，折實呎價最低為第2座15樓E室，屬兩房戶，實用面積393平方呎，折實售價約721.54萬元，折實呎價約18,360元。折實呎價最高則為第2座26樓J室，同屬兩房戶，實用面積339平方呎，折實售價約717.26萬元，折實呎價約21,158元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>同柱比較 實際加幅僅約1.28%至3.79%</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第2號價單折實均呎雖較首張價單高約6.83%，但主要因為今次以高層單位為主，拉高整體均呎。若以同柱單位比較，實際加幅僅約1.28%至3.79%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以第2號價單中的第2座22樓G室為例，折實呎價為19,327元；對比首張價單中同柱的21樓G室，折實呎價為18,620元，兩者相差約3.79%，考慮到高層單位的樓層差價及景觀差異後，發展商是次開價屬原價加推。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nByt9JmSXYUI2kskv2O4ig--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/f6930516eb8051f5dddd5c941c13cf71\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>2號與1號價單比較：第2座22樓與21樓G室</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>項目背景</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首岸第1期位於紅磡庇利街1號，由恒基兆業、希慎興業、帝國集團及市建局合作發展。項目提供360伙，實用面積由301至642平方呎，戶型涵蓋兩至三房戶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交通方面，項目步行至港鐵土瓜灣站約8分鐘。校網方面，物業屬小學35校網，中學校網則為九龍城區。項目預計關鍵日期為2027年8月31日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"首匯\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:首匯;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/首匯\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">首匯</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"首岸\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:首岸;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/首岸-33812\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">首岸</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"太古城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:太古城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/太古城-27352\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">太古城</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"九龍城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:九龍城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/九龍城-27371\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">九龍城</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"土瓜灣\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:土瓜灣;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/土瓜灣-27389\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">土瓜灣</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"紅磡\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:紅磡;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/紅磡-27387\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">紅磡</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E9%A6%96%E5%B2%B8%E7%AC%AC1%E6%9C%9F%E5%8E%9F%E5%83%B9%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A8120%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%9D%87%E5%91%8E19-940%E5%85%83-%E5%90%8C%E6%9F%B1%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E5%8A%A0%E5%B9%85%E7%B4%841-28-%E8%87%B33-79-75637\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
