        {
            "title": "財經｜騰訊QClaw海外內測爆紅  每日免費派4000萬token吸客",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜騰訊QClaw海外內測爆紅 每日免費派4000萬token吸客\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜騰訊QClaw海外內測爆紅 每日免費派4000萬token吸客</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">騰訊（0700）旗下熱門AI智能體QClaw正式開啟海外版內測，首批覆蓋美國、加拿大、新加坡、韓國、澳洲等熱門市場，支援中英法西韓日六大語言及WhatsApp、Telegram、Discord三大通訊平台，零門檻即裝即用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">產品承襲內地版「極簡基因」，僅用5天開發完成，99%代碼由QClaw自主生成，內測期每日免費派發4000萬token（單日最高值約700美元），首批2萬個創始龍蝦（Founding Claw）限量名額3小時內搶光。內地版3月10日上線短短10天突破100萬用戶，現累計數億活躍基礎助攻海外擴張，內置Agent Playground提供健身教練、金融分析師、語言導師等20款專業AI代理，一鍵搞定複雜任務。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ea25bc4a-558b-352a-8b59-026dc20c7954-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">騰訊同時宣布成OpenClaw官方贊助商，QClaw將深度整合龍蝦開源框架，目標年底用戶破10億，挑戰ChatGPT全球霸主地位。市場看好此舉將推升騰訊AI市值，股價昨微升0.8%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8Aqclaw%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%85%A7%E6%B8%AC%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E6%B4%BE4000%E8%90%ACtoken%E5%90%B8%E5%AE%A2-074432257.html",
